Basic idea behind map implementation is any string of size one is a palindrome and a string can be palindrome only if has any previous occurance, so store the indexes of all the previous occurances in a map and check for palindrome.

1. we can iterate through the given string once 
2. read each charecter one by one and see if it has any previous occurance
3. if its not first occurance check if the substring is returning as palindrome
4. check the maximum length size and return the substring which has maximum length.

